column2: SELECT  g.objid as objid, g.ra, g.dec, zns.nvote, zns.p_el as elliptical, zns.p_dk as dontknow, zns.p_mg as merger, g.petror9#_r as petror9#_r, g.fiberMag_g as fiberMag_g, S.velDisp as velDisp, g.g, fiberMag_g+#*log1#(#) as fiberSB_g FROM Galaxy as G JOIN ZooNoSpec AS zns ON G.objid = zns.objid join SpecObj as S on G.objid = S. bestObjID WHERE g.clean=# and zns.nvote >= # and zns.p_el > # AND s.z < # AND velDisp > #.
